{"article_id":"7rF7SqpJN2YVeC5E","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A bipartisan immigration proposal has surfaced in the Senate ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"only to be quickly knocked down by President Donald Trump via Twitter on Monday .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Republican Sen. John McCain and Democratic Sen. Chris Coons planned to propose legislation Monday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that would shield from deportation immigrants","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"who entered the U.S. illegally as children ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"known as \" Dreamers \"","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"helped by the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program , or DACA .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"The bill also would strengthen border security ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"but it wouldn ' t provide the $ 25 billion","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Trump wants for a U.S.-Mexico border wall .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"before the Senate had a chance","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"to consider the narrow plan ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Trump seemed to reject it on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" Any deal on DACA","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that does not include STRONG border security and the desperately needed WALL","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"is a total waste of time .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"March 5th is rapidly approaching","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and the Dems seem not to care about DACA .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"Make a deal ! \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Any deal on DACA","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that does not include STRONG border security and the desperately needed WALL","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"is a total waste of time .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"March 5th is rapidly approaching","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and the Dems seem not to care about DACA .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Make a deal !","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"February 5 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"McCain , R-Ariz. , and Coons , D-Del. , said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that their bill was designed","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"to focus on two \" pressing \" border issues","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"- the \" Dreamers \" and border security -","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"so lawmakers could focus on completing a long-overdue budget deal .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"The McCain-Coons plan is a more modest approach","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"than Trump has sought","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"for protecting the estimated 1.8 million young immigrants .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The measure lacks Trump ' s demands","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"for limiting the relatives","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that \" Dreamers \" can sponsor for citizenship ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and ending a visa lottery","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"aimed at admitting more immigrants from diverse places","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"including Africa .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"The senators ' plan would create a road to legal status for \" Dreamers \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"who arrived in the U.S. by the end of 2013","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and meet other criteria ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"including no convictions for serious crimes .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Once they ' ve become lawful permanent residents ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"they can follow existing procedures","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to apply for citizenship .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Democrats and some Republicans want to give \" Dreamers \" a pathway to citizenship ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"but oppose cuts","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Trump would make","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"in the number of legal immigrants","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"allowed to enter the U.S.","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Conservatives oppose letting \" Dreamers \" become citizens .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"That stalemate has led many to believe","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"the likeliest outcome is a narrowly focused bill or even no legislation at all .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The senators ' proposal is similar to a bipartisan House package by Reps. Will Hurd , R-Texas , and Pete Aguilar , D-Calif .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"READ MORE :","depth":3},{"id":62,"text":"What ' s in the White House ' s latest immigration plan ?","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":122,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":64,"right":121,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":91,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":75,"right":90,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":71,"right":74,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":68,"right":70,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":3,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":66,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":4,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":8,"right":69,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":11,"right":72,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":87,"right":89,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":81,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity"